sources.title: Freeze | Full Movie | Action Survival Horror
sources.description:
Freeze - On a rescue mission to the North Pole in 1905, to retrieve an old friend and his lost expedition crew , Captain Mortimer and his crew are set upon by bloodthirsty fish-creatures, leaving the survivors stranded in a frozen wilderness being hunted down.
2022.  Stars: Johnny Vivash, David Lenik, Beatrice Barrilà
